## System Architecture
================================================================================

**Telephony**: Asterisk (Docker) + Twilio SIP trunk
**Bots**: 20 AVR Core instances (ports 9092-9111)
**Voice Pipeline**: Deepgram STS (Speech-to-Speech)
**Orchestrator**: Python dialer_orchestrator.py
**Database**: SQLite (dialer.db)
**Dashboard**: React (port 3003 dev, 8002 prod)
**API**: FastAPI (port 8000)

**Call Flow**:
1. Orchestrator triggers AMI Originate
2. Asterisk dials via Twilio (PJSIP)
3. On answer, redirects to bot extension
4. AudioSocket streams audio to AVR Core
5. AVR Core connects to Deepgram STS WebSocket
6. STS handles full conversation (ASR→LLM→TTS)
7. Audio streams back through AudioSocket to caller

